Hey_Bloody - Salsa-thirsty ,
Among those Salsa places in Saigon , CHANH_BISTRO_ROOFTOP has been proving its attraction to all Salseras and Salseros in Saigon . Not too noisy , but yet the dynamic playlist and dancer have never get boring dancing on this rooftop . So what do we got ? ; )
+ A super cool location on Rooftop 6 floor provided an amazing view at every corner of Saigon ( nearby Bitexco )
+ A new emerged DJ Trong_Khoi_Nguyen , who ' s earning good feeling of dancers in town .
+ A place provided activity : game with prize , workshop , special events and so on to help you decide easily : " Yes , I ' ll definitely go to Chanh this Thursday "
+ Food & drink from 5 star hotel standard guarantee to please every fastidious customer ; )
What cha waiting for ? bring your ass here and enjoy your Thursday night at Chanh_Bistro_Rooftop_Saigon B - )
• Location : Chanh_Bistro_Rooftop_Saigon ( 6th Floor , 43-45 Ho_Tung_Mau , Ben_Nghe_Ward , Dist . 1 )
• Time : 9pm – 12am
• Ticket entrance : 60.000 VND ( 01 drink included )
PS : For those who come by Bike and park in our basement , please give the ticket to receptionist for applied free parking : D
See you at # ChanhBistroRooftop and “ let your ass rock the dance floor ” \ m / \ m /
